Subject: RE: [T2] odd tool, help id?

That is a tool for turning off water supply near the meter.  Rural houses have
shut off valves approximately 3 feet below the ground surface as opposed to
inside the basement.  That tool makes it a ton easier than trying to reach
down with a crescent wrench.

